title: The Draymond Green Show - Mahomes Magic, Russ Trade Rumors + a Zach LaVine Interview
itunes:title: The Draymond Green Show - Mahomes Magic, Russ Trade Rumors + a Zach LaVine Interview
description:
In the tenth episode of The Draymond Green Show, Draymond discusses the incredible divisional round of the playoffs, Russell Westbrook trade rumors, and James Harden free agency rumors before welcoming on Zach LaVine to discuss him and DeMar Derozan leading the Chicago Bulls to a hot start, the 2020 Tokyo Olympics, his dunk contest experience, and much more.
